        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "For the matter of that I say what I think, and I care very little whether others think as I do.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133212_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133212/543_133212_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "\"There would not be much harm in that,\" said Martin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "\"It is a great question,\" said Candide.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Candide did not quite agree to that, but he affirmed nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Paquette continued her trade wherever she went, but made nothing of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "\"Ha!\" said Pangloss to Paquette, \"Providence has then brought you amongst us again, my poor child!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "\"Hold your tongue,\" answered the Dervish.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Their little plot of land produced plentiful crops.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_133217_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/133217/543_133217_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "\"All that is very well,\" answered Candide, \"but let us cultivate our garden.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "The future has been filled with fear, stained and polluted by the heartless past.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Why should we fear that which will come to all that is?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "We cannot tell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "We do not know which is the greatest blessing, life or death.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Every cradle asks us \"Whence?\" and every coffin \"Whither?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "The largest and the nobler faith in all that is, and is to be, tells us that death, even at its worst, is only perfect rest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "My Friends: I am going to do that which the dead often promised he would do for me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "He had not passed on life's highway the stone that marks the highest point, but being weary for a moment he lay down by the wayside, and, using his burden for a pillow, fell into that dreamless sleep that kisses down his eyelids still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "While yet in love with life and raptured with the world, he passed to silence and pathetic dust.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000008_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000008_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "He loved the beautiful and was with color, form and music touched to tears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-543_137106_000009_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/543/137106/543_137106_000009_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-543",
        "content": "Speech can not contain our love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
